HEADWORD: Flavol
<hw>Fla"vol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>flavus</ets>
yellow + <ets>-oil</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A yellow,
crystalline substance, obtained from anthraquinone, and regarded as a
hydroxyl derivative of it.</def>⟦br⟧
